page.title: 14HOME + FAMILY IN CARLISLE<1>
page.content: My house was built in 1971,so it is 14 years old.It's quite a big house.It has six rooms,two downstairs and four upstairs.We have a kitchen,a living room,a bathroom,three bedrooms and a hall.It is a semidetached house.We have a big garden with a lot of plants and flowers in it.We do not have a garage but we have a shed.We have gas central heating.I have lived here for eleven years.My mum and dad have lived here for 14 years. 2 In my family there are four people: my mam,my dad,my sister and I.My sister is Morag,or Moogie or Boo for short.I always fight with her if she comes in my bedroom.My mam works as a midwife at the City Maternity Hospital She works on nights,so she has to sleep through the day.My dad works at the family practitioner committee. <CONTINUED ON NEXT PAGE>
